        <p>In 2024, ATAC's lean budget helped build the coalition that passed SB 1507—a reform impacting 40,000 incarcerated Arizonans. In 2025, with expanded funding, Praxis Initiative runs five programs and will train 75 returning citizen advocates. Your donation scales this impact. <strong>Monthly donors</strong> provide predictable funding that lets us hire directly impacted staff, plan multi-year campaigns, and guarantee stipends for every training cohort.</p>
        <p>Major gifts ($5,000+) fund strategic expansion. A recent $10,000 donation allowed us to expand <strong>ARTS in Prison & Think Motion</strong> to ASPC-Tucson. Corporate sponsorships ($25,000+) underwrite our advocacy days and training programs. Legacy gifts ensure Arizona always has a directly impacted voice at the table. Whatever the size, your donation seeds power in communities historically denied it.</p>
